  m_TableData:
  - m_Id: 58963357696
    m_Localized: "<b>At McDonald\u2019s, we promote and maintain a safe, respectful
      and inclusive workplace for everyone by:</b>"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32415523106816
    m_Localized: Manager's Role in Building a Safe, Respectful, and Inclusive Workplace
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 280336076206080
    m_Localized: <size=+20><b>Manager's Role in Building a Safe, Respectful, and
      Inclusive Workplace</b>
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 300762370240512
    m_Localized: Living and championing our values every day
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 301541340573696
    m_Localized: Treating everyone with respect
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 324650974146560
    m_Localized: Being aware and reflecting on the impact that our words and actions
      have on others
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 328896373157888
    m_Localized: Speaking up when you see or experience inappropriate behavior
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 329567763787776
    m_Localized: Remembering everyone, especially leaders, plays a key role in creating
      a respectful culture
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2592079758446592
    m_Localized: 'As a manager of others, you have a critical role in building a
      safe, respectful, and inclusive workplace.


      You are expected to be a
      role model for your team and always lead by example!'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2592417236340736
    m_Localized: <b>Managers have a responsibility when it comes to being a role
      model, including:</b>
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2592760418488320
    m_Localized: Setting a positive example by ensuring your conduct, including your
      employment decisions and workplace behaviors, are free of inappropriate behaviors
      such as harassment (physical, psychological, sexual), discrimination, bullying
      and retaliation/victimization.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2593642577088512
    m_Localized: Taking steps to eliminate all inappropriate behaviors such as harassment
      (physical, psychological, sexual), discrimination, bullying and retaliation/victimization.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2594270552477696
    m_Localized: Immediately escalating when you become aware of any inappropriate
      conduct or if an employee provides you with information about behavior that
      could make them, or others feel uncomfortable or unsafe.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2594492410187776
    m_Localized: Taking allegations or reports seriously on all inappropriate behaviors
      such as harassment (physical, psychological, sexual), discrimination, bullying,
      and retaliation/victimization.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2595063053635584
    m_Localized: Partnering with the right people to investigate allegations promptly
      and thoroughly.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2595208877002752
    m_Localized: Ensuring you and your team members know how and where to speak up
      if they experience or recognize inappropriate behavior.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609365743521792
    m_Localized: <b>What do you think you should do in this situation?</b>
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609551664435200
    m_Localized: '<b>Someone has come to you with a possible complaint.

      What
      do you think you should do in this situation?</b>'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609684217024512
    m_Localized: Select all the applicable cards.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2610809649451008
    m_Localized: Thank the person for coming forward.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2610878549282816
    m_Localized: Take the complaint seriously.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2610915408826368
    m_Localized: Listen, but do not take sides or draw conclusions.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2610968991059968
    m_Localized: Explain that someone will follow up.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2611299066007552
    m_Localized: 'A young employee has told you that a supplier winked at them and
      it made them feel uncomfortable.


      Is the following response from a manager
      appropriate?'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2611431417270272
    m_Localized: Adam
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2611612242104320
    m_Localized: "\u201CThat supplier winks at everyone, but they\u2019re harmless.\nIf
      they do something more serious, you can always come to us to let us know.\u201D"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2611893193363456
    m_Localized: Correct! Managers should always take potentially inappropriate conduct
      seriously. This means reporting the incident immediately.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2612031949328384
    m_Localized: Incorrect, managers should always take potentially inappropriate
      conduct seriously. This means reporting the incident immediately.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2612287864786944
    m_Localized: What should you do if an employee tells you they witnessed inappropriate
      language from a senior leader towards crew members?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2612453514629120
    m_Localized: Wait to observe if the senior leaders' behavior happens again.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2612574507716608
    m_Localized: "Explain to the crew members that it can happen sometimes, and it\u2019s
      not a big deal."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2612620355653632
    m_Localized: Say that the senior leader's conduct is not tolerated and report
      it.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2612676479635456
    m_Localized: "Correct! As a manager, you have discretion in stopping inappropriate
      behavior. Any inappropriate behavior, including senior leaders' behaviors\_must
      be reported and taken seriously."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2612770310410240
    m_Localized: Incorrect, as a manager, you have discretion in stopping inappropriate
      behavior. Any inappropriate behavior, including senior leaders' behaviors must
      be reported and taken seriously.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2612922806915072
    m_Localized: "An employee complains to you that a manager harassed them because
      they returned late from a break for the second time this week. The manager
      took them aside to discuss the issue and gain a commitment to being punctual.\n\_\nIs
      this harassment?"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2613051878232064
    m_Localized: "Correct! Communicating McDonald\u2019s expectations and taking
      aside an employee to discuss an issue is not a form of harassment. However,
      it could be harassment if the feedback was delivered in a forceful, hurtful,
      threatening or intimidating way. If you\u2019re unsure, you should report it
      through the proper channel."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2613344506433536
    m_Localized: "Incorrect, communicating McDonald\u2019s expectations and taking
      aside an employee to discuss an issue is not a form of harassment. However,
      it could be harassment if the feedback was provided in a bullying way. If you\u2019re
      unsure, you should report it through the proper channel."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2613459648466944
    m_Localized: "<b>Manager\u2019s Responsibilities Around Retaliation/Victimization</b>"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2613561855266816
    m_Localized: Retaliation/victimization occurs when someone is punished or experiences
      a negative employment or individual action because they intend to, or have
      raised a complaint, or are involved in a complaint (such as a witness) about
      workplace behavior such as potential harassment (physical, psychological, sexual),
      discrimination, bullying, or retaliation/victimization.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2613610907652096
    m_Localized: "<b>Examples of retaliation/victimization:</b>\n\n\u2022<indent=5%>Termination</indent>\_\n\u2022<indent=5%>Demotion\_</indent>\_\n\u2022<indent=5%>Poor
      Performance Review\_\_</indent>\n\u2022<indent=5%>Changing shifts</indent>\n\u2022<indent=5%>Excluding
      from teams, events, meetings\_</indent>\n\u2022<indent=5%>Undesirable tasks\_\_</indent>"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2613718365720576
    m_Localized: As a manager - prevent, stop, and report any retaliatory behaviors
      from your team. If, as a manager, you are accused of retaliation/victimization,
      continue managing the employee as a role model. Cooperate fully and honestly
      with investigators and let the process run its course.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2613822434791424
    m_Localized: "As a manager \u2013 prevent, stop, and report any retaliatory behaviors
      from your team."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2613934519177216
    m_Localized: "In the following scenario, Samuel reported his co-worker, Miguel,
      for inappropriate behavior. Now, some of Samuel\u2019s co-workers are not speaking
      to him. Samuel has confronted them about why he had to report Miguel, but his
      co-workers are still ignoring him.\_\_\n\_\nAfter noticing the tension, Anna,
      the manager, sits down for a chat with Samuel."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2614011002310656
    m_Localized: Anna
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2614046637117440
    m_Localized: You all used to be friends, and the vibe around here was fantastic.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2614120544948224
    m_Localized: Samuel
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2614198881964032
    m_Localized: Yeah, well things change.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2614224014233600
    m_Localized: In this situation, can Anna transfer Samuel to a new restaurant?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2614313474543616
    m_Localized: "Correct!\_It\u2019s clear that Anna wants to transfer Samuel to
      another restaurant based on the fallout from Samuel\u2019s complaint. Changing
      an employee\u2019s work situation because the employee made a complaint is
      extremely risky, even if the manager and the employee consider it a positive
      move.\n\_\nA good rule of thumb is to treat an employee the same as if they
      never made a complaint."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2614433234505728
    m_Localized: "Incorrect,\_it\u2019s clear that Anna wants to transfer Samuel
      to another restaurant based on the fallout from Samuel\u2019s complaint. Changing
      an employee\u2019s work situation because the employee made a complaint is
      extremely risky, even if the manager and the employee consider it a positive
      move.\n\_\nA good rule of thumb is to treat an employee the same as if they
      never made a complaint."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2614603657465856
    m_Localized: It can be difficult for people to come forward with a complaint.
      Acknowledge that difficulty by thanking them.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2615178197422080
    m_Localized: There are many reasons why people might not report (for example,
      fear that their report might not be taken seriously).
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2615219234492416
    m_Localized: Only collect the information required to make the report with compassion
      and objectivity.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2615270258200576
    m_Localized: Establishing expectations during the reporting process is key.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2616712327024640
    m_Localized: Someone who makes a complaint or is involved in the investigation
      of a complaint can often feel insecure and even threatened.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2616952182493184
    m_Localized: "Speaking up for each other puts people first, creates inclusion,
      and it\u2019s the right thing to do.\_\_"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2616995702591488
    m_Localized: "<b>When to Speak Up</b>\n\_\nNot sure when it\u2019s the right
      thing to do?\_\n\_\nAsk yourself these questions about the situation:"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2617243074252800
    m_Localized: Am I offended by what I see?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2617462226636800
    m_Localized: Could this go against our values?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2617526504345600
    m_Localized: "Does any person look uncomfortable?\_"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2617569235914752
    m_Localized: Does watching this make me uncomfortable?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2617613712314368
    m_Localized: "If your answer to any of these questions is \"Yes,\" it\u2019s
      a good idea to speak up."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2617686349271040
    m_Localized: '<b>There are four ways to speak up. Anyone can utilize these four
      ways depending on the situation and their comfort level.


      Flip each
      card for more information.</b>'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2617762022903808
    m_Localized: "<b>Be Direct:</b> \nIdentify the correct action or behavior.\_"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2617816230088704
    m_Localized: "<b>Redirect:</b> \nBring up a new topic and redirect the conversation."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2617852200439808
    m_Localized: '<b>Delay:</b>

      Address the behavior or discomfort at a more
      neutral time.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2617899503800320
    m_Localized: "<b>Seek Assistance:</b>\nAs a manager, you can seek guidance.\_"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2617962007318528
    m_Localized: <b>Which of the following should you do if you witness any form
      of inappropriate conduct from a customer toward an employee?</b>
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2618062515425280
    m_Localized: "Tell the customers that \u201Cwe appreciate your visit but we want
      you to know that we can\u2019t have inappropriate language here.\u201D"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2618343659622400
    m_Localized: "Make sure to take sole responsibility for getting the customer\u2019s
      order prepared."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2618387137777664
    m_Localized: At the first opportunity, tell the employee that the customer's
      conduct is not tolerated here and report it.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2618432058773504
    m_Localized: Wait to mention what you observed till it is more convenient.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2618481622863872
    m_Localized: As a manager, you have discretion in stopping inappropriate behavior.
      Any inappropriate behavior must be reported and treated seriously.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2618524257964032
    m_Localized: Incorrect, as a manager, you have discretion in stopping inappropriate
      behavior. Any inappropriate behavior must be reported and treated seriously.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2618619523190784
    m_Localized: <b>Why Speak Up?</b>
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2618729158103040
    m_Localized: "Speaking up aligns with our values:\n\n\u2022<indent=5%>Puts people
      first</indent>\n\u2022<indent=5%>Creates inclusion</indent>\n\u2022<indent=5%>Strengthens
      our community/work family</indent>\n\nIt\u2019s also the right thing to do."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2618858913091584
    m_Localized: "Remember, when you speak up, you:\_\n\n\u2022<indent=5%>Take the
      first step to stopping any inappropriate behavior</indent>\n\u2022<indent=5%>Act
      as a role model of our values </indent>\n\u2022<indent=5%>Encourage others
      to come forward with concerns</indent>"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2618964798296064
    m_Localized: Speak Up to create a culture of belonging where each person has
      a voice and trusted ally.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2619046234902528
    m_Localized: <b>Interacting with Employees</b>
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2619095698329600
    m_Localized: "\u2022<indent=5%>It can be risky for managers to socialize with
      employees outside of the workplace. Socializing can often start out well, but
      becoming overly familiar has the potential to impact your judgment.</indent>\n\n\u2022<indent=5%>If
      you treat people differently, you risk creating an environment that can be
      perceived as discriminatory. That can create a hostile work environment for
      those who don\u2019t feel favored.</indent>\n\_\n\u2022<indent=5%>Favoritism
      includes giving preferential treatment to one or more employees, causing others
      to lose out on possible job promotions or benefits like better shifts.</indent>"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2619130938871808
    m_Localized: "If you treat people differently, you risk creating an environment
      that can be perceived as discriminatory. That can create a hostile work environment
      for those who don\u2019t feel favored.\n\_\nFavoritism includes giving preferential
      treatment to one or more employees, causing others to lose out on possible
      job promotions or benefits like better shifts."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2619167324459008
    m_Localized: Always be aware that actions and words, even away from work, can
      later affect the work environment.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2619225725947904
    m_Localized: "\u2022  Always be aware that actions and words, even away from
      work, can later affect the work environment.\n\n\u2022  Review and acknowledge
      the policy where you work regarding managers socializing with employees outside
      of work.\n\n\u2022  Stop and think before socializing outside of work with
      other employees."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2619266410696704
    m_Localized: Stop and think before socializing outside of work with other employees.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2619331070087168
    m_Localized: Be mindful when communicating with other employees through text
      messages or other social media channels.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2619509646774272
    m_Localized: Any interactions with co-workers via text messages or social media
      should be respectful and professional.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2619554618101760
    m_Localized: Avoid posts that could reasonably be viewed as malicious, obscene,
      threatening, or intimidating.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2619588357083136
    m_Localized: Do not post or support any posts that include discriminatory remarks
      or content, harassment (physical, psychological, sexual), threats of violence,
      or similar inappropriate or unlawful conduct.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2619636767739904
    m_Localized: Managers must exercise caution and sound judgment if interacting
      with employees via text messages or social media.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2619668753502208
    m_Localized: Participating in such forums with subordinates may increase the
      potential to violate our values. Think before you post anything and always
      ask for consent.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2619733047988224
    m_Localized: Additionally, avoid interacting on social media with employees under
      the age of 18.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2619797409583104
    m_Localized: <b>Abuse of Authority</b>
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2619884999233536
    m_Localized: "\u2022  An example of abuse of authority is misconduct that involves
      a person with authority (such as a manager, supervisor or other authority figure)
      making promises, denying, or threatening a job benefit or making decisions
      in exchange for sexual favors.\n\n\u2022  Such behaviors violate our values
      and do incredible damage to everyone involved."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2619924635406336
    m_Localized: Such behaviors violate our values and do incredible damage to everyone
      involved.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2619964825227264
    m_Localized: "\u2022  Abuse of authority is not limited to exchanging favors
      for sex. Any activity promised in exchange for a favor (such as a date, a kiss,
      or a hug) is inappropriate and not tolerated by McDonald\u2019s.\n\n\u2022 
      Abuse of authority isn\u2019t categorized by the gender of the offender or
      victim. Regardless of the genders involved, it\u2019s absolutely unacceptable
      to sexually harass anyone or abuse your authority."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2620003890974720
    m_Localized: "Abuse of authority isn\u2019t categorized by the gender of the
      offender or victim. Regardless of the genders involved, it\u2019s absolutely
      unacceptable to sexually harass anyone or abuse your authority."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2620054579138560
    m_Localized: <b>Abuse of authority also includes treating someone less favorably
      because they reject offers of sexual activity or favors.</b>
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2620149190053888
    m_Localized: "<b>Threats</b>\n\n\u2022   Termination\n\u2022   Demotion\_\n\u2022  
      Poor performance review\_\n\u2022   Changing shifts\n\u2022   Excluding from
      teams, events, meetings\n\u2022   Undesirable tasks\n\u2022   Delegating the
      same tasks (mopping, cleaning) only to certain employees"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2620257784778752
    m_Localized: "<b>Promises</b>\n\n\u2022   Continued employment\_\n\u2022   Promotion\_\n\u2022  
      Positive performance review\_\n\u2022   Additional overtime"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2620348922810368
    m_Localized: '<b>Conclusion


      In your role, you have a responsibility to:</b>'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2620484646293504
    m_Localized: Report all inappropriate behavior.</indent>
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2620514086113280
    m_Localized: Speak up when you see inappropriate behavior.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2620555144155136
    m_Localized: Encourage your team to speak up if they see or experience inappropriate
      behavior.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2620572621819904
    m_Localized: Prevent or stop any retaliation/victimization.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2620609611386880
    m_Localized: Stop and think before you socialize outside of work with employees.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2620668432306176
    m_Localized: Be aware of your impact on the work environment and avoid favoritism.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2620709704257536
    m_Localized: Exercise caution when communicating with co-workers via social media
      and text messages.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2620743099305984
    m_Localized: "Don\u2019t abuse your authority."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2620798967435264
    m_Localized: '<b>Reminder</b>

      If you have any questions regarding these
      points, please review your local policies and ask for advice.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4631539316781056
    m_Localized: Explain that someone will follow up.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4633439663648768
    m_Localized: Do not promise confidentiality or make promises.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4633509599473664
    m_Localized: Report immediately, seek advice, and be discreet.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4633596132159488
    m_Localized: Offer your personal opinion on the situation to show empathy.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
